{
  "stem": "11179.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some of them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the-- the cleaning supply store was called [NON-ENGLISH], Water Bird.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that was evidently the name of the people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was one chain store I remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There were other Jewish chain stores.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Winston ?] department stores.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But after that initial, that boycott day, I think it was in April 1 or something, 1933-- I'm not sure exactly when it was.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Most of these major businesses, the Jewish people, left.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Sold it, evidently.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I really am ignorant about what they did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were not boycotted, per se.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And while there were incidents evidently all during those years, I haven't seen any in Berlin until November the-- the-- the 10, 1938, when they smashed the windows of-- a lot of Jewish business was single stores.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But they did have chain stores.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I can't think of-- of a name of-- or any other, except the department stores.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was Tietz, Wertheim, and so on, which is still existing under that name.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Karstadt, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the five and ten.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There were several.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] and so on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they were-- they were not just in Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They were also in Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I don't know, even in other-- in other countries.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I know they were in Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I really don't remember too much about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know I did read-- read a little bit in the newspapers, I mean, little incidents and things like that when I-- when I was about 10 years old, 11 years old.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I did read some of the news.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I did read sometimes something in the newspaper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Radio, my parent's radio broke.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
